thread.title: Russell Kelley

author: Russell Kelley
title: Russell Kelley
text: Site prompts definitely improve my ability to get the job done, I bought the correct sockets based on the what you might need prompts and also picked up the rotor set screws turned out I needed both. Site organization is definitely a step above most and with next day shipping and living as close as I do I get most parts within a week. I have never had a bad experience to date, their customer service is also top notch, very communicative and quick to resolve any issues.
